==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Palatalize
<hw>Pal"a*tal*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <fld>(Phon.)</fld>
<def>To modify, as the tones of the voice, by means of the palate;</def>
<specif>especially:</specif> <def>to pronounce a consonant with the
tongue against the palate; <as>as, to <ex>palatalize</ex> a letter or
sound</as>; to palatize. See <er>palatalized</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>palatalized</ent>⟦br⟧
